channel.title: Inferno - No Slogan, Much Wow
channel.description:
[FONT=Microsoft Sans Serif] [SIZE=7][COLOR=orange]Inferno[/COLOR][/SIZE] Inferno is a 474 runescape private server. Our goal is to bring a server which is not easy. The economy will be very well done. We hope to bring the features you all want to see, this will be including absolutely Flawless pking. Yes, FLAWLESS PKING. A Feature a lot of servers lack in is the ability to go in the wilderness and kill people flawlessly. The economy will be a good strong economy, Everyone will NOT be running about with all the most expensive armour, i think this will make it fair for the new generation oh players. There will be Tons of bosses because people like bosses. It is a feature that will attract the PvMers. There will be a lot of quests that benifit people, including some really nice items that can only be obtained through that quest(s). All skills should be fully working on release day. We will have an achievement system to really make things worth doing for example some people like killing rockcrabs, Why not make it that you can kill 100 rock crabs and receive a player title 'Rock Killer'. More information will be added soon [CENTER][img]http://i416.photobucket.com/albums/pp250/Randall835/homehb.png[/img] [center][SIZE=4][COLOR=orange]Please Enjoy these Recent Screenshot[/COLOR][/SIZE] [img]http://i.imgur.com/fVlFF8t.png[/img] [img]http://i.imgur.com/yBF2ksm.png[/img] [SIZE=4][COLOR=orange]Our Drop Simulators - What our npc's drop[/COLOR][/SIZE] [spoiler="click here"] [img]http://i.imgur.com/Syoyrjq.png[/img] [img]http://i.imgur.com/JMfWm07.png[/img] [/spoiler] [SIZE=4][COLOR=orange]Developers[/COLOR][/SIZE] [url=http://rune-server.org/members/Optimum]Special Air service (me)[/url] [url=http://rune-server.org/members/Iwan]Iwan[/url] [url=http://rune-server.org/members/Keiron]Keiron[/url] [SIZE=4][COLOR=orange]What our website looks like[/COLOR][/SIZE] [spoiler="click here"] [img]http://i.imgur.com/duONOoY.jpg[/img] [img]http://i.imgur.com/lXKTlbW.png[/img] [/spoiler]
[FONT=Microsoft Sans Serif][SIZE=5][COLOR=orange]Recent Changes[/COLOR] [spoiler=click here] [b]6/16/2014[/b] - fixed bug where you couldnt pick stackables with full invent - Fixed bug where you could walk when picking - pickable : wheat, cabbage, onions, flax, roses [b]6/15/2014[/b] - Made a drop simulator for testing drops - New and improved drop table - fixed the drops bug [b]6/14/2014[/b] - Fixed very rare drops, now perfect - Fixed drops bug, rarearity was less than what it was - some npc's have been fixed - Fixed NPC and player clipping - Ring of wealth has been added - the real effect only applies to rare drop table - Over 275 NPC's now access the rare drops table [b]6/13/2014[/b] - A few client updates - Purple sweets have been added - Added a new Npc Rare drop table, this feature will drop a random item from the rare drop table - Fixed a few issues with drops crashing server - Fixed a ton of bugs with the drop system - Rewritten Drop System - Common - uncommon - rare - very rare [b]6/12/2014[/b] - Karambwan has no delay when used with other foods - Karambwan's are now edible - Dragon dagger fixed -when before got 0 hp it would show 0 - Control panel added new features - Dragon dagger has been modified -spec now hits 1 then after 600 seconds it hits another one [b]6/11/2014[/b] - Karambwan cooking has been added - Karambwan fishing has been tweaked [b]6/10/2014[/b] - Control panel has been added [b]6/9/2014[/b] - Quest tab has been fixed - Fixed running, now you will stop running instantly when you have 0 energy - Proper Energy Method - Added a Dismantale - Fixed up Karambwan Fishing Adjusted Timer - Added Ladder Climbing - Added New Quest Interface [b]6/8/2014[/b] - Added new Drop announcements - Added global announcment method - Added the start of a Wealth generated - Karambwan Fishing Fully finished Timers perfect - Karambwan Fishing Adjusted and tweaked - karambwan fishing has been added - Fixed Full invy deleting 1 item and getting 1 item temporary - Constant drops fixed - Items now appear when you drop them - Fixed a few bugs with Teleporting - New Drop System is implimented and ready to test - Changed default clan to Help - New Starting, Brings you to the tuturial island - Teleports fixed when in the Tuturial Island - Home Teleport changed - Spawn Locations changed - Start location changed [/spoiler] [SIZE=5][COLOR=orange]Features[/COLOR][/SIZE] [spoiler=click here] A flawless Drop System - Unique drops to that npc and over 250 have access to the rare drop table [/spoiler] [SIZE=5][COLOR=orange]Media[/COLOR][/SIZE] [spoiler=click here] [img]http://i.imgur.com/yBF2ksm.png[/img] [img]http://i.imgur.com/7jw5kjv.png[/img] [img]http://i.imgur.com/pBnFbzB.gif[/img] [img]http://i.imgur.com/7jw5kjv.png[/img] [img]http://i.imgur.com/pBnFbzB.gif[/img] [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/TSiUOI7.png[/img] [img]http://i.imgur.com/DU11dSD.png[/img] [img]http://i.imgur.com/XWSFa6u.png[/img] [img]http://i.imgur.com/jPImbQ9.png[/img] [/spoiler] [/center]
